                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1071" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE WESTON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant F</hi> 6.) I found this bottle of gin in the saw-dust.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> Did you hear his master say it was no use to deny it, he had better tell the truth? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> I heard something of that kind said, but I was searching round the cellar.</p>
